### HomeBase Bot System - REST API Tests
### Run with REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071/api

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# BOT MANAGEMENT
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List all bots
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots HTTP/1.1

### Get bot signals (recent opportunities/alerts)
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots/signals?limit=20 HTTP/1.1

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# MANUAL BOT EXECUTION
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Run ALL bots manually (quick scan)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/run-all HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Run specific bot: Price Alert
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/demo-price-alert/run HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Run specific bot: Opportunity Detector
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/demo-opportunity/run HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Run specific bot: SMA Crossover
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/sma-crossover-bot/run HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PAPER TRADING
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get paper trading portfolio
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots/portfolio HTTP/1.1

### Paper trade: BUY $100 of Bitcoin
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/portfolio/trade HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "side": "buy",
  "coinId": "bitcoin",
  "amountUsd": 100
}

### Paper trade: BUY $50 of Ethereum
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/portfolio/trade HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "side": "buy",
  "coinId": "ethereum",
  "amountUsd": 50
}

### Paper trade: BUY $25 of Solana
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/portfolio/trade HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "side": "buy",
  "coinId": "solana",
  "amountUsd": 25
}

### Paper trade: SELL all Bitcoin
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/portfolio/trade HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "side": "sell",
  "coinId": "bitcoin"
}

### Paper trade: SELL specific amount of ETH
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/portfolio/trade HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "side": "sell",
  "coinId": "ethereum",
  "coinAmount": 0.25
}

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CRYPTO PRICES (existing endpoint)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get default prices (BTC, ETH, SOL)
GET {{baseUrl}}/crypto HTTP/1.1

### Get specific coins
GET {{baseUrl}}/crypto?ids=bitcoin,ethereum,solana,cardano,polkadot HTTP/1.1

### Get meme coins
GET {{baseUrl}}/crypto?ids=dogecoin,shiba-inu,pepe,bonk,floki HTTP/1.1

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# HEALTH CHECK
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Health endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/health HTTP/1.1
